            <title><![CDATA[[抓狂]#头发到底多久洗一次好# 医学期刊《皮肤附属物紊乱》研究显示，每天洗头与7天不洗头相比，头皮瘙痒会减少，发质也不会受到明显损伤，只要洗头方法正确，每...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[抓狂]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_zhuakuang-c007ffb7fe.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%A4%B4%E5%8F%91%E5%88%B0%E5%BA%95%E5%A4%9A%E4%B9%85%E6%B4%97%E4%B8%80%E6%AC%A1%E5%A5%BD%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%A4%B4%E5%8F%91%E5%88%B0%E5%BA%95%E5%A4%9A%E4%B9%85%E6%B4%97%E4%B8%80%E6%AC%A1%E5%A5%BD%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#头发到底多久洗一次好#</span></a> 医学期刊《皮肤附属物紊乱》研究显示，每天洗头与7天不洗头相比，头皮瘙痒会减少，发质也不会受到明显损伤，只要洗头方法正确，每天洗头也不会比少洗头掉发更严重。<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[话筒]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/o_huatong-0a3e80b147.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>卫子建议：油性发质每1-2天洗一次；中性和干性发质每2-4天洗一次。<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E6%9D%A5%E8%BE%9F%E8%B0%A3%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E6%9D%A5%E8%BE%9F%E8%B0%A3%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫来辟谣#</span></a><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%E7%B4%A0%E5%85%BB%E6%8F%90%E5%8D%87v%E8%AE%A1%E5%88%92%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%E7%B4%A0%E5%85%BB%E6%8F%90%E5%8D%87v%E8%AE%A1%E5%88%92%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#健康素养提升v计划#</span></a>  （科普中国）<br><br>问题来了，你会每天洗头吗<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[doge]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/d_doge-be7f768d78.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span> <a href="http://t.cn/A6WRAVUx" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_web_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span> <span class="surl-text">网页链接</span></a>]]></description>
