            <description><![CDATA[【被群蜂围攻！一女子身上多处受伤！<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[话筒]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/o_huatong-0a3e80b147.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>医生提醒：登山时要注意】近日，伍女士在公园登山时随手拍死一只正在叮咬自己的小黄蜂，不料却被一群黄蜂追着叮咬！伍女士顿时感觉头晕、呕吐、呼吸不畅，路人紧急拨打了120。经过深圳市第三人民医院的治疗，目前伍女士已经脱离生命危险，回家修养。<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[衰]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_shuai-285d2d97c7.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>👇🏻<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a>（西部决策） <a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4968325541986346" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">深圳卫健委的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/orj480/a8bfee30gy1hjvpf8j8b8j20f00qodgf.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/u0/B7kHzTwrgx08abL9O7he01041200873H0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=540x960.24.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1700125464&amp;ssig=BotuCJc3L3&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/u0/lXQNtEcEgx08abL9qy4o010412004sKo0E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=360x640.24.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1700125464&amp;ssig=qTyxvM%2BaXF&amp;KID=unistore,video"><p>视频无法显示，请前往<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034%3A4968325541986346" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">微博视频</a>观看。</p></video>]]></description>
